schema.title: cargo-mutants config
schema.description:
cargo-mutants configuration, read by default from `.cargo/mutants.toml`.

See <https://mutants.rs/>.

additional_cargo_args.description: Pass extra args to every cargo invocation.

additional_cargo_test_args.description: Pass extra args to cargo test.

build_timeout_multiplier.description: Build timeout multiplier, relative to the baseline 'cargo build'.

copy_vcs.description: Copy `.git` and other VCS directories to the build directory.

error_values.description: Generate these error values from functions returning Result.

examine_globs.description: Generate mutants from source files matching these globs.

examine_re.description: Examine only mutants matching these regexps.

exclude_globs.description: Exclude mutants from source files matching these globs.

exclude_re.description: Exclude mutants from source files matches these regexps.

minimum_test_timeout.description: Minimum test timeout, in seconds, as a floor on the autoset value.

skip_calls.description:
Skip calls to functions or methods with these names.

This is combined with values from the --skip-calls argument.

skip_calls_defaults.description: Use built-in defaults for `skip_calls` in addition to any explicit values.

test_package.description: Run tests from these packages for all mutants.

test_tool.description: Choice of test tool: cargo or nextest.

test_workspace.description:
Run tests from all packages in the workspace, not just the mutated package.

Overrides `test_package`.

timeout_multiplier.description: Timeout multiplier, relative to the baseline 'cargo test'.

TestTool.description: Choice of tool to use to run tests.
